<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.5.2">
<l>pārit teḻunta paṭaimaṉṉar tammai yāḷa pāratattut</l>
<l>tēril pāka ṉāyūrnta tēva tēva ṉūrpōlum</l>
<l>nīril paṇaitta neṭuvāḷaik kañcip pōṉa kurukiṉaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>āral kavuḷō ṭarukaṇaiyu maṇiyār vayalcū ḻaḻuntūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of the god of gods who mounted the chariot as a driver</l>
<l>In the Bhārata [War], to rule kings who hoisted their weapons,</l>
<l rend="indent">raising [them high],</l>
<l>It seems is Aḻuntūr surrounded by beautiful paddy fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where flocks of herons,</l>
<l>Which had fled, fearing the long, fat vāḷai [fish] in the water,</l>
<l rend="indent">gather closely together with āral [fish] in their beaks.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
